---
version: 8.0.1
layout: census-website/views/_master
---

{% from "components/card/_macro.njk" import onsCard %}

{% block page %}
{% from "census-website/components/call-to-action/_macro.njk" import onsCallToAction %}
{{-
    onsCallToAction({
        "headingText": "Ready to start your census survey?",
        "paragraphText": "You'll need the access code from the letter we sent you.",
        "button": {
            "text": "Start survey",
            "classes": 'btn--small'
        }
    })
}}
<div class="page__container container {{ containerClasses }}">
        {% from "components/breadcrumb/_macro.njk" import onsBreadcrumb %}
            {{ 
                onsBreadcrumb({
                    "ariaLabel": 'Breadcrumb',
                    "itemsList": [
                        {
                            "url": '/prototypes/census-website/',
                            "text": 'Home'
                        },
                        {
                            "url": '/prototypes/census-website/help/',
                            "text": 'Help with your census'
                        },                        
                        {
                            "url": '',
                            "text": 'How to complete your census',
                                "current": true                                                

                        }
                    ]
                }) 
            }}
    <div class="grid">
        <div class="grid__col col-7@m">
            <main id="main-content" class=" {{ pageClasses }}">
                <h1 class="u-mb-l u-fs-l">How to complete your census</h1>
                {#
                <div class="u-mb-xs" style="font-weight:bold;">Contents</div>
                <ul class="list list--bare">
                    <li>— Overview</li>
                    <li>— <a href="/prototypes/census-website/help/how-to-complete-the-census/who-should-complete/">Who should complete the census</a></li>
                </ul>
                <div class="u-mt-l">
                        <hr class="footer__hr" style="margin-bottom: 0;">
                </div>
                #}
            </main> 
            <div class="u-mt-s">
                <main id="main-content" class=" {{ pageClasses }}">
                    
                    <p>We will send a letter to your household asking the householder to complete the census.</p>
                    {% from "components/details/_macro.njk" import onsDetails %}
                    {{
                        onsDetails({
                            "id": "details",
                            "title": "What is a household and who is the householder?",
                            "classes": "u-mb-m",
                            "content": "<p>A <strong>household</strong> is either:</p>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li>one person living alone</li>
                                            <li>a group of people (who don't have to be related) living at the same address who share cooking facilities and share a living or dining area</li>
                                        </ul>
                                        <p>The <strong>householder</strong> is a person who individually or jointly:</p>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li>owns or rents the property</li>
                                            <li>is responsible for paying the household bills and expenses</li>
                                        </ul>",
                            "button": {
                                "close": "Hide this"
                            }
                        })
                    }}
                    <p>To complete your census online, use the unique access code in the letter we sent the householder.</p>
                    <p>Complete your census as soon as possible.</p>
                    <p>It should take between 20 to 30 minutes to complete. You can save your answers and return to them later if you need to.</p>
                    {% from "components/panel/_macro.njk" import onsPanel %}
                    {{-
                        onsPanel({
                            "body": "Keep your unique access code safe as you will need it each time you return to the survey.",
                            "classes": "u-mb-m"
                        })
                    }}

                    <p>For help completing your census online, or to request a paper questionnaire, <a href="/prototypes/census-website/contact-us">contact us.</a></p>
                    <h3 class="u-fs-m">I have not seen a census letter</h3>
                    <p>If you are the householder, you can <a href="/prototypes/census-website/contact-us">request a new census letter.</a></p>
                    <p>If you are not the householder, you will need the unique access code to complete your individual questions. Speak to the householder to see if they have the census letter with the unique access code.</p>
                    <p>This may not be possible, or you may not want the people you live with to see your answers. You can <a href="https://deploy-preview-28--sdc-prototypes.netlify.com/prototypes/rh-census/address.html">request a code to respond separately</a>. We will send you a new access code by text.</p>
                    
                </main>
            </div> 
            <div class="u-mt-l">
                        <hr class="footer__hr" style="margin-bottom: 0;">
                </div>  
            
            <div class="u-mt-s">
                <div class="grid__col col-4@m" style="padding-left:0;">
                
                </div>
                <div class="grid__col col-4@m push-4@m col-5@xs push-1@xs" style="padding-left:0;">
                  <a href="online/" style="text-align:right;"><h2 class="u-mb-xs">Next ></h2><p>Online</p> </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="grid__col col-4@m push-1@m">
            <div style="border-top:5px solid purple;padding:15px 0;">
                <h3>Related content</h3>
                    <ul class="list list--bare">
                        <li><a href="#">About the census</a></li>
                        <hr>
                        <li><a href="#">Contact us</a></li>
                    </ul>
            </div>
        </div>      
    </div>
</div>
{% endblock %}
